name: Emily Ratajkowski Embedding
description:
Emily O'Hara Ratajkowski (born June 7, 1991) is an American model and former actress. Born in London to American parents and raised in Encinitas, California, Ratajkowski began her career as a child actor appearing in two episodes of the Nickelodeon series iCarly (2009–2010). Her modeling debut was on the cover of the March 2012 issue of the erotic magazine treats!, which led to her appearing in two music videos: Robin Thicke's "Blurred Lines" and Maroon 5's "Love Somebody".
